com.example.booknet

Class MockDatabase

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.booknet.DatabaseManager
      • com.example.booknet.MockDatabase

  • public class MockDatabase
extends DatabaseManager
    A fake memory based database for testing the activities. Uses the same function signatures as the real database but overrides their functions.
    Author:
    Jamie

    DatabaseManager
